# Caprese Salad

## Ingredients
- Tomatoes
- Mozzarella di buffala 
- Extra Virgin Olive oil 
- Oregano (fresh or dried)

## Instructions
- Cut the tomatoes in disk slices.
- Cut the mozzarella in disk slices or tare (as wished)
- Compile the tomati and mozzarella slices 
- Drizzle extra virgin olive oil.
- sprinkle with the oregani
